        "en": "Foreign matter <5.01>—The amount of ovaries, stems, leaves and other foreign matter contained in Safflow-er does not exceed 2.0z. Total ash <5.01> Not more than 18.0z."
      }
    }
  ],
  "storageConditions": {
    "en": "Containers—Well-closed contain-ers."
  }
